│ intrinsic, getVectorIntrinsicIDForCall returns Intrinsic::not_intrinsic (0).  │
│ Passing that into VPWidenIntrinsicRecipe leads to later calls to VectorUtils  │
│ asserting. This contradicts VPRecipeBuilder::tryToWidenCall, which correctly  │
│ guards intrinsic handling with ID != not_intrinsic and otherwise chooses a    │
